SMS,Telintel,is,a,platform,for,designing,creating,and,managing,services,that,are,provided,via,SMS,messaging,Such,services,may,include,marketing,campaigns,PR,campaigns,games,opinion,polls,etc,One,component,of,this,platform,is,the,Bulk,SMS,service,which,enables,users,to,send,an,SMS,message,to,a,large,group,of,recipients,with,a,single,command,The,Bulk,SMS,service,can,be,fully,integrated,with,the,user,s,software,services,and,websites,through,the,RESTful,SMS,Telintel,API